                <a href="/reviews/platforms/brightside" class="block w-full text-center bg-brand-secondary-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-brand-secondary-700 transition font-medium">View Full Review</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Understanding Depression - Enhanced */}
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border-2 border-neutral-100 p-8 md:p-12 mb-16 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-8">Understanding Depression and Online Treatment</h2>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-white rounded-xl border border-green-100 p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                <div class="w-1 h-6 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></div>
                Types of Depression Treated Online
              </h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                Online therapy effectively treats various forms of depression:
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-3">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                  <span class="text-neutral-700"><strong class="text-neutral-900">Major Depressive Disorder:</strong> Persistent low mood, loss of interest, and energy changes</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                  <span class="text-neutral-700"><strong class="text-neutral-900">Persistent Depressive Disorder:</strong> Chronic depression lasting two years or more</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                  <span class="text-neutral-700"><strong class="text-neutral-900">Seasonal Affective Disorder:</strong> Depression related to seasonal changes</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                  <span class="text-neutral-700"><strong class="text-neutral-900">Postpartum Depression:</strong> Depression following childbirth</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-white rounded-xl border border-blue-100 p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                <div class="w-1 h-6 bg-blue-500 rounded-full"></div>
                Evidence-Based Treatment Approaches
              </h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                Effective online therapy for depression uses these proven approaches:
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-3">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                  <span class="text-neutral-700"><strong class="text-neutral-900">Cognitive Behavioral Therapy (CBT):</strong> Addressing negative thought patterns and behaviors</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                  <span class="text-neutral-700"><strong class="text-neutral-900">Interpersonal Therapy:</strong> Improving relationships and communication patterns</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                  <span class="text-neutral-700"><strong class="text-neutral-900">Behavioral Activation:</strong> Increasing engagement in meaningful activities</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                  <span class="text-neutral-700"><strong class="text-neutral-900">Medication Management:</strong> Antidepressants when appropriate, combined with therapy</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-primary-50 to-white rounded-xl border border-brand-primary-100 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
              <Shield class="h-6 w-6 text-brand-primary-600" />
              Why Online Therapy Works Well for Depression
            </h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
              Online therapy offers unique advantages for depression treatment:
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 p-4 hover:shadow-md transition">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-brand-primary-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                  <div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-1">Lower Barrier to Entry</h4>
