              <div class="bg-brand-primary-100 rounded-full w-14 h-14 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                <Brain class="h-7 w-7 text-brand-primary-600" />
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Severity Level</h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
                Consider the severity of your depression symptoms. Mild to moderate depression often responds well to therapy alone, while severe depression may benefit from combined therapy and medication.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-50 to-white rounded-xl border border-accent-100 p-6 hover:shadow-md transition">
